description: Enad Global 7 AB engages in the development and marketing of digital games. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 563 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-12-06. The firm develops games for a range of platforms, including PC, Mac, Linux, PS3, PS4, X360, XONE, iOS, Android Mobile and Android Consoles. The firm uses Autodesk Stingray game engine to build games. Toadman Interactive AB operates within two business areas: Game Development and Consulting. The Game Development implies development of own games, such as Immortal: Unchained. The Consulting business area comprises tailor-made consulting services for both developers and publishers worldwide, including support on different phases of process, such as game design, programming and graphics.
name: Enad Global 7 AB (publ)
